@node dt2ps "PostScript PlugIn: About dt2ps"

                                  About dt2ps
                                 -------------

   dt2ps is a Stand-Alone-Shelltool without GUI that reads in pictures via
   picture.datatype (including v43-TrueColor-Support) and outputs postscript.

   Since the PostScript-Print-PlugIn is based on dt2ps, they both share the same
   outputengine and have mostly the same features.

   dt2ps can be found in Aminet: util/dtype/dt2ps.lha

@endnode
